➜景德镇市浮梁县举办10·17扶贫日电商直播带货大赛活动
http://www.sohu.com/a/425641470_159678	38814
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——助力脱贫攻坚 线上线下尽显其能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201019/a45fa211b595455c81e6b9ed68d6c0a7.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">共同按下启动球</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201019/7774f18f3dc643bd9f9514fde6edb74b.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">浮梁县副县长周民生致辞</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201019/e13314e856c54dc0bc84467f868d2125.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">电商主播代表分享直播经验</span></img></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
